ANATOMY DATA NOTICES
--------------------

A1 anatomy (VMR0066 — Vascular Model Repository):
  See data/anatomy/a1_vmr0066/LICENSE_VMR0066 for the VMR data license.
  The VMR license permits redistribution with attribution.
  When using this anatomy in publications, cite:
    N.M. Wilson et al., "The Vascular Model Repository," J. Med. Devices 7(4), 2013.
    doi:10.1115/1.4025983

A2/A3 anatomies (ASOCA):
  Not bundled. ASOCA data is distributed under a registration-gated research
  license that does not permit redistribution. Users must register (free) at
  https://asoca.grand-challenge.org/ and run scripts/download_asoca.py.
